From: Drew Fustini <dfustini@baylibre.com>
Date: Wed, 6 Dec 2023 00:09:24 -0800
Subject: [PATCH 059/400] riscv: dts: thead: Enable LicheePi 4A eMMC and
 microSD

Add emmc node properties for the eMMC device and add sdio0 node
properties for the microSD slot. Set the frequency for the sdhci
reference clock.

Signed-off-by: Drew Fustini <dfustini@baylibre.com>
Reviewed-by: Guo Ren <guoren@kernel.org>
Signed-off-by: Drew Fustini <dfustini@tenstorrent.com>
Link: https://lore.kernel.org/r/20231206-th1520_mmc_dts-v8-4-69220e373e8f@baylibre.com
Signed-off-by: Han Gao <gaohan@iscas.ac.cn>
---
 .../dts/thead/th1520-lichee-module-4a.dtsi    | 20 +++++++++++++++++++
 1 file changed, 20 insertions(+)

diff --git a/arch/riscv/boot/dts/thead/th1520-lichee-module-4a.dtsi b/arch/riscv/boot/dts/thead/th1520-lichee-module-4a.dtsi
index f674e5acd0f9..8e3d0fd94647 100644
--- a/arch/riscv/boot/dts/thead/th1520-lichee-module-4a.dtsi
+++ b/arch/riscv/boot/dts/thead/th1520-lichee-module-4a.dtsi
@@ -33,6 +33,10 @@ &apb_clk {
 	clock-frequency = <62500000>;
 };
 
+&sdhci_clk {
+	clock-frequency = <198000000>;
+};
+
 &uart_sclk {
 	clock-frequency = <100000000>;
 };
@@ -47,6 +51,22 @@ &dmac0 {
 	status = "okay";
 };
 
+&emmc {
+       bus-width = <8>;
+       max-frequency = <198000000>;
+       mmc-hs400-1_8v;
+       non-removable;
+       no-sdio;
+       no-sd;
+       status = "okay";
+};
+
+&sdio0 {
+       bus-width = <4>;
+       max-frequency = <198000000>;
+       status = "okay";
+};
+
 &gpio0 {
 	gpio-line-names = "", "", "", "", "", "", "", "", "", "",
 			  "", "", "", "", "", "", "", "", "", "",
